Create the kafka topic befor running the producer:
/usr/bin/kafka-topics --create --bootstrap-server x.x.x.x:9092 --replication-factor 1 --partitions 3 --topic topic_name

Other operations:
/usr/bin/kafka-topics --describe --bootstrap-server x.x.x.x:9092 --topic topic_name
/usr/bin/kafka-topics — zookeeper x.x.x.x:2181 — delete — topic topic_name

Requirement for running producer
install boto3: https://pypi.org/project/boto3/   

boto requires aws cli to install:
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/cli/latest/userguide/cli-chap-install.html  

run "aws config" to set credentials
https://forums.aws.amazon.com/thread.jspa?threadID=141985  

